    "Following this, the paper summarizes the issues and challenges in the ACOSQE domain, such as data scarcity, expression ambiguity, and implicit sentiment recognition.",
    "It proposes potential solutions and suggestions to address these challenges and enhance ChatGPT's capabilities in SA.",
